brainRegion.label: Ventral anterior-lateral complex of the thalamus

_source.description: This is a morphology reconstruction of a mouse thalamus cell that was obtained from the Janelia Mouselight project http://ml-neuronbrowser.janelia.org/ and was used in part or in whole to construct some of the cells used in the circuit of (Iavarone, et al., 2023) https://doi.org/10.1016/j.celrep.2023.112200 . This morphology is positioned in the Mouselight custom "CCFv2.5" reference space, instead of the Allen Institute CCFv3 reference space.
_source.name: AA0579 in CCFv2.5
